article_title: Typhoon Neoguri Crawls Toward Main Japanese Islands After Sweeping Over Okinawa
article_text:
TOKYO—Typhoon Neoguri was gradually losing force as it approached Japan's southernmost main island of Kyushu on Wednesday after pummeling the Okinawa island chain with torrential downpours that flooded streets and homes in the prefecture and triggered landslides.
